= Robotrek (SNES) - Inventions =

This page documents the invention system in Robotrek.

== Overview ==

The invention system is the core mechanic of Robotrek. Players use materials collected from enemies and treasure to create items and equipment for their robots.

== Invention Mechanics ==

=== Components Required ===

Each invention requires 2-4 materials:
* '''Primary''' - Main component (defines type)
* '''Secondary''' - Modifier (affects stats)
* '''Tertiary''' - Optional (special abilities)
* '''Catalyst''' - Rare items (unique inventions)

=== Success Rate ===

{| class="wikitable"
! Inventor Level !! Base Rate !! Per Level
|-
| 1-10 || 50% || +3%
|-
| 11-20 || 80% || +2%
|-
| 21-30 || 100% || --
|}

Failure uses materials but produces "Junk".

